    <item>
      <title>小麦和棉花价格暴跌，因交易商权衡经济衰退和风暴风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/wheat-and-cotton-slump-as-traders-weigh-recession-storm-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员评估经济衰退风险和热带风暴黛比的威胁，小麦和棉花等农产品价格周一暴跌，尽管抛售程度不如其他全球金融领域那么严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/wheat-and-cotton-slump-as-traders-weigh-recession-storm-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 16:49:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波动率指数创纪录飙升 华尔街交易员全押注市场平静</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/record-vix-spike-rocks-wall-street-traders-all-in-on-market-calm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一资产市场的暴跌正重创一系列押注股市将维持平静的衍生品交易，有可能引发连锁反应，从而加剧全球动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/record-vix-spike-rocks-wall-street-traders-all-in-on-market-calm</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 16:38:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>硅谷银行破产计划获批，但 20 亿美元 FDIC 纠纷仍未解决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/svb-ends-bankruptcy-but-dealt-a-setback-in-2-billion-fdic-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名法官批准了硅谷银行金融集团的重组协议，但却使该公司在与联邦监管机构的斗争中遭遇挫折，该斗争旨在收回去年硅谷银行子公司倒闭时所持有的约 20 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/svb-ends-bankruptcy-but-dealt-a-setback-in-2-billion-fdic-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 15:16:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉信理财、富达交易员报告称股票崩盘期间出现中断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/schwab-fidelity-traders-report-outages-amid-market-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[零售经纪公司嘉信理财公司 (Charles Schwab Corp.) 和富达投资 (Fidelity Investments) 周一报告称，在全球股市抛售期间出现了服务中断的情况，不过两家公司都表示，他们的问题已在下午早些时候得到解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/schwab-fidelity-traders-report-outages-amid-market-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:21:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>信贷恐慌指数大幅下跌，迫使企业借款人退避三舍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/asia-high-grade-dollar-bond-spreads-widen-the-most-in-22-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，全球主要信用风险指标飙升，因人们对经济增长放缓的担忧日益加剧。这场动荡实际上导致美国公司债券销售停滞，而这原本是一年中最繁忙的日子之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/asia-high-grade-dollar-bond-spreads-widen-the-most-in-22-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:22:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街受恐慌情绪影响 经济陷入“危险区域”：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对世界最大经济体增长放缓的担忧引发人们警告称，今年的股市火爆涨势已过度，全球市场再度出现波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
